import React from "react";
import Container from "react-bootstrap/Container";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import Image from "react-bootstrap/Image";

function ImageGallery() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Row>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=First" thumbnail />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=First" thumbnail />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=First" thumbnail />
        </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=First" thumbnail />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=First" thumbnail />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=First" thumbnail />
        </Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x300?text=First" thumbnail />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="holder.js/200x200" thumbnail />
        </Col>
        <Col xs={4} md={4}>
          <Image src="holder.js/200x200" thumbnail />
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default ImageGallery;
